  Cold-start works! The mapper routes unseen tasks to appropriate blocks using only the task description:
  - MultiRC (QA) gets 50% accuracy — routed to similar blocks as BoolQ/SQuAD
  - CNN/DailyMail gets 21.6 ROUGE-L — routed to similar blocks as XSum

  This validates TaskMap's core advantage over Direct BL: generalization to unseen tasks without any task-specific training.

